                    Use these details to receive local {selectedWallet.currency} bank transfers. Funds will be credited to your Zerah wallet automatically.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <button className="w-full bg-primary text-background-dark py-5 rounded-[24px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest shadow-xl shadow-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 active:scale-95 transition-all">
                  <span className="material-icons-round">share</span>
                  <span>Share Account Details</span>
